1.0.0-alpha5.name: drupal/oox_ostream

security-coverage.message: Project has not opted into security advisory coverage!

1.0.0-alpha5.description: Provide interface based API for handling objects into streams. These streams can fetch any kind of objects and can be used in order to make your code persistence agnostic. Entity support is unstable and may not work, nevertheless some other default implementations are provided.
